            <title>[AVRO-1971] AvroAlias Annotation should work on field elements</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AVRO-1971</link>
                <project id="12310911" key="AVRO">Apache Avro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;@AvroAlias annotation works only for records / classes but not for fields when using ReflectData-generated schemas. The specification allows aliases for comple types AND for fields.&lt;/p&gt;
